original_title: Élie Kakou : Vidéo pirate du Zénith
overview: Discover for the first time on DVD, the video pirate at the Zenith of Elie Kakou. An original show in an overexcited atmosphere with amazing choreographies, a surprise visit from Michel Drucker and parodies of Elie's sketches by the "Compagnie des Sales Gosses".
title: Élie Kakou : Vidéo pirate du Zénith
